        "content": "<p>Answering a bit of your question: <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=SimpleGraph.adjMatrix#doc\">docs#SimpleGraph.adjMatrix</a> is a matrix with \"index type\" the vertex set of the simple graph</p>",
